[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0361","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0361.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0442","title":"Qualcomm Qpopper EUIDL 命令格式字符串本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Qpopper 2.53 及更早版本中存在格式化字符串漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在邮件 From: 头部中构造特制的格式化字符串，当 euidl 命令处理该头部时触发漏洞，导致攻击者获取系统特权。该漏洞影响 Cobalt RaQ 2.0/3.0 及 qpopper 2.52/2.53 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至 qpopper 2.53 以上版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0442"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:44.560","remediation":"升级 Qpopper 至 2.54 及以上版本，该版本修复了 euidl 命令处理 From: 头时的格式化字符串漏洞。如无法升级，可在 qpopper.conf 中禁用 euidl 命令（设置 allow-euidl = no），并限制本地用户对 POP3 服务的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0267.html","http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/suse_security_announce_51.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1242","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19955","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0442.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0442","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0442.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0442.json","https://github.com/freebsd/freebsd-ports/blob/6d99a569fc5f92410614c124a0a3ccfd4a5644ea/security/vuxml/vuln/2003.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f37077e857e7a28bab83d284c23299407fb1af7e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fff4-6jqp-pqh2/GHSA-fff4-6jqp-pqh2.json","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-04/SRC%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E6%8C%96%E6%8E%98%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%2B%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E7%AF%87.md","https://github.com/illuusio/freebsd-osv/blob/3234f9e67d0170ff9c6cada9a1f48f061b109728/md/2003/FreeBSD-2003-0004.md","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/freebsd_qpopper_253_1.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0442.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0361.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0326","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0326.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0396","title":"Pacific Software Carello 文件复制与源代码披露漏洞","description":"Pacific Software 的 Carello 购物车软件 1.2.1 版本中 add.exe 程序存在文件复制漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过特制请求复制服务器上的任意文件，进而读取 .ASP 等 Web 脚本的源代码，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Carello 1.2.1 及更早版本，攻击复杂度低，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0396"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-24","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Pacific Software Carello 1.2.1 已停止维护，无官方补丁可用。建议立即在 Web 服务器（IIS）URL 重写规则中禁止访问 /scripts/Carello/add.exe，或直接删除 add.exe 文件以消除源代码泄露风险。长远应迁移至仍在维护的购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0285.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1245","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19957","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0396.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0396","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0396.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0396.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-73vq-vfrf-93x8/GHSA-73vq-vfrf-93x8.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-misc.rules","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0396.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001403.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0326.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0326.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0343","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0343.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0418","title":"Cayman 3220-H DSL路由器 ICMP Ping of Death 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cayman 3220-H DSL 路由器在处理 ICMP Echo 请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何认证即可向目标设备发送超大的 Ping 数据包，由于设备未对 ICMP 报文长度进行有效校验，超长数据包将触发内存溢出，导致路由器服务崩溃、重启或无响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞属于经典的 Ping of Death 攻击变种，攻击条件简单，仅需目标可达即可实施，影响所有 Cayman 3220-H DSL 路由器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0418"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-23","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该路由器型号已停产且无官方补丁，建议更换支持 ICMP 报文长度校验的现代路由器。若无法更换设备，应在网络边界防火墙配置 ACL 规则，丢弃长度超过 65535 字节的 ICMP Echo Request 数据包以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0280.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1240","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/324"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0343.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0358","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0358.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0438","title":"多款Linux发行版 fdmount 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux 系统中 fdmount 工具存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，该工具用于挂载软盘设备且允许 floppy 组成员使用。当 fdmount 处理超长的 mountpoint 参数时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者能够覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 S.u.S.E Linux 4.x/5.x/6.x/7.0、Slackware 3.x/4.0、Turbolinux 6 及 OpenLinux 7.0 等多个发行版本。本地攻击者只需获取 floppy 组成员权限，传入特制的长参数即可利用此漏洞实现权限提升至 root。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0438"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:44.043","remediation":"建议立即移除 fdmount 的 setuid 权限：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/fdmount`；或彻底卸载 fdmount 软件包。对于受影响的老旧发行版（SuSE/Slackware/Turbolinux 等），建议升级至不受影响的版本或改用现代发行版。如业务必须使用 fdmount，应限制仅可信用户加入 floppy 组。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0245.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1239","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19954","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0438.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0438","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0438.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0438.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fg2g-48g8-4xwm/GHSA-fg2g-48g8-4xwm.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e333a498-73f8-4d6b-a227-25c89776a724.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001400.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0358.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0355","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0355.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0436","title":"MetaProducts Offline Explorer 目录遍历漏洞","description":"MetaProducts Offline Explorer 1.2 及更早版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向应用程序发送包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 URL 请求，绕过路径访问限制读取目标系统上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Offline Explorer 1.0/1.1/1.2 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，可能导致敏感系统文件泄露。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0436"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:43.747","remediation":"升级 MetaProducts Offline Explorer 至 1.3 或更高版本，该版本修复了路径遍历问题。如无法升级，避免使用 Offline Explorer 下载来自不可信来源的网站内容，并在代理或防火墙层面对出站请求进行路径规范化过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0254.html","http://www.metaproducts.com/mpOE-HY.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1231","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19945","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0436.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0436","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0436.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0436.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xhhr-v6vq-6mcw/GHSA-xhhr-v6vq-6mcw.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0436.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001397.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--944525ab-849c-4942-8184-0957c2155d54.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0355.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0263","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0263.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0305","title":"Microsoft Windows IP 碎片重组拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 4.0/2000 及 Terminal Server 系统的 IP 碎片重组模块存在资源管理错误漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标系统发送大量内容相同的 IP 分片数据包（即 Jolt2 攻击），即可导致目标系统 CPU 占用率飙升、系统响应缓慢甚至完全崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响范围广泛，攻击条件简单，利用代码已公开，危害等级高。微软已在 MS00-029 安全公告中发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0305"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:26.387","remediation":"安装微软 MS00-029 安全更新补丁，或升级至 Windows XP 及以上版本。对于仍运行 Windows 2000 的系统，在防火墙规则中丢弃入站 IP 分片数据包可临时缓解。这些操作系统均已停止支持，建议尽快升级至受支持的 Windows 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1236","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/advisory.html?id=2240","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-029","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/214"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0263.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0356","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0356.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0437","title":"CyberPatrol cyberdaemon 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CyberPatrol 的 cyberdaemon 组件中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该服务运行于 Gauntlet 防火墙（4.1/4.2/5.0）、WebShield E-ppliance（100.0/300.0）以及 IRIX 6.5.x 系统中。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标发送特制请求触发溢出，导致服务拒绝响应或执行任意命令。该漏洞影响范围涉及多家厂商的多款安全产品，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0437"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:43.900","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Gauntlet Firewall 4.1/4.2/5.0、WebShield E-ppliance 100.0/300.0 及 IRIX 6.5.x 中的 CyberPatrol 守护进程 cyberdaemon。厂商 PGP 和 TIS 已发布安全公告并提供补丁，建议立即升级到修复版本。由于上述产品均已停止技术支持，强烈建议迁移至受支持的最新防火墙产品。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙限制对 cyberdaemon 服务端口（默认 TCP 端口）的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0249.html","http://www.osvdb.org/322","http://www.pgp.com/jump/gauntlet_advisory.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1234","http://www.tis.com/support/cyberadvisory.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19949","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0437.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0437","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0437/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0437.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0437.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrqj-pqq8-9fx3/GHSA-mrqj-pqq8-9fx3.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b